::DrillBit::

The electricity from the trident was heading for DrillBit.
"Computer, reconfigure energon dampers for electricity."
-Request confirmed-
The electricity hit his body but caused no damage, except a scorch mark
or two.
"Computer, feed back electricity at origin."
-Request confirmed-
The electricity then shot back at Depth Charge, followed by 50cal.
gattaling gun fire.
